data.title: Tatiana Stepa
data.meta_description: Tatiana Stepa was a Romanian folk singer.
data.text:
Tatiana Stepa (April 21, 1963 – August 7, 2009) was a Romanian folk singer.

Quick Facts Born, Died ...

Close

Born in Lupeni, she attended the High School for Architecture in Bucharest and made her debut in 1982 with Cenaclul Flacăra at the Făgăraș stadium.[1]
